OL,3,CJury in Gerry Adams' libel case to
OL,4,Cresume deliberations on Friday morning
OL,6,FThe jury in Gerry Adams' libel action
OL,7,Fagainst the BBC will continue
OL,8,Fdeliberations on Friday morning.
OL,10,FFormer Sinn Fein leader Mr Adams
OL,11,Falleges a BBC Spotlight programme, and
OL,12,Fan accompanying online story, defamed
OL,13,Fhim by alleging he sanctioned the
OL,14,Fkilling of former Sinn Fein official
OL,15,FDenis Donaldson, for which he denies
OL,16,Fany involvement.
OL,18,FMr Donaldson was shot dead in Co
OL,19,FDonegal in 2006, months after
OL,20,Fadmitting his role as a police and MI5
OL,21,Fagent over 20 years.
