OL,6,FIn the programme broadcast in
OL,7,FSeptember 2016, an anonymous source
OL,8,Fgiven the pseudonym Martin claimed the
OL,9,Fshooting was sanctioned by the
OL,10,Fpolitical and military leadership of
OL,11,Fthe IRA and that Mr Adams gave "the
OL,12,Ffinal say".
OL,14,FIn 2009, the dissident republican
OL,15,Fgroup the Real IRA claimed
OL,16,Fresponsibility for the killing and a
OL,17,FGarda investigation into the matter
OL,18,Fremains ongoing.
