OL,3,CJury in Gerry Adams' libel case to
OL,4,Cresume deliberations on Friday morning
OL,6,FTrial judge Mr Justice Alexander Owens
OL,7,Fsent the jury out to begin
OL,8,Fdeliberations at 10.25 on Thursday
OL,9,Fmorning, in the fifth week of
OL,10,Fproceedings.
OL,12,FThe 12 members were provided with
OL,13,Fexhibits in the case and the means to
OL,14,Fre-watch the programme, and advised
OL,15,Fthey could continue to discuss the
OL,16,Fcase during lunch.
OL,18,FAt one stage in the deliberations, one
OL,19,Fof the jurors was released from the
OL,20,Fprocess due to other commitments,
OL,21,Fincluding a camogie match.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
