OL,6,FThe BBC had argued that the jury
OL,7,Fshould not find that this was the
OL,8,Fmeaning of the words, instead saying
OL,9,Fthe claim had been put forward as an
OL,10,Fallegation that was immediately
OL,11,Ffollowed by Mr Adams' denial.
OL,13,FIf the jury agrees with the
OL,14,Fbroadcaster on this point, it has no
OL,15,Ffurther considerations or decisions to
OL,16,Fmake.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
