OL,6,FThe BBC had argued to the jury that if
OL,7,Fit got to this point, it should award
OL,8,Fonly nominal damages.
OL,10,FMr Owens told the jury that the
OL,11,Fbroadcaster had put forward the
OL,12,Fposition that Mr Adams had "no
OL,13,Freputation at all".
OL,15,FIt is open to the jury to award one
OL,16,Feuro at that point.
